    "description": {
      "value": "<strong>Kineticist Element</strong><br/><br/><p>Kineticists who focus on the element of fire are called pyrokineticists. Pyrokineticists wield elemental fire as a potent weapon, and they possess a powerful offense.</p><p><b>Class Skills: </b>A pyrokineticist adds Escape Artist and Knowledge (nature) to her list of class skills.</p><p><b>Wild Talents</b></p><p>Simple Blast - fire blast</p><p>Composite Blasts - blue flame blast, magma blast, plasma blast, steam blast, summer blast</p><p>Defense - searing flesh</p><p>1st - basic pyrokinesis, burning infusion, cold adaptation, dazzling infusion, energize weapon, fan of flames, fire sculptor, fire's fury, heat adaptation</p><p>2nd - fire steed, flame trap, foxfire, penetrating infusion, searing flame</p><p>3rd - eruption, firesight, flame jet, foxfire infusion, heat wave, smoke storm, torrent</p><p>4th - detonation, flash infusion, purifying flames</p><p>5th - elemental transmission, fire corridor, flame jet, greater, flame shield, improved fire steed, trail of flames, unblinking flame infusion, unraveling infusion</p><p>6th - brilliant infusion, purging flame</p><p>7th - explosion, pure-flame infusion</p><p>8th - greater fire steed</p><p>9th - from the ashes</p>",
